reviewText: We were a little disappointed by the fact that this got such high reviews and no one bothered to mention that these were repeats.  We thought this would be like some of the other dvd's ie: Mexico, Vampire, Alien invaders, Loch Ness Monster.  Our daughters still enjoyed watching them but kept saying,"Not a new show."  But it still hasn't stopped them from watching it.  I am just disappointed that we were ripped off and bought a dvd with repeat shows....well buyer beware!!!!  Otherwise I would have given it a 5 star as per the kids.
summary: These shows are on the other DVD's Season 1, 2 and 3

reviewText: This video completed our set of What's New Scooby Doo (10 DVD Set includes: Space Ape on the Cape, Safari So Good, Halloween Boos and Clues, Merry Scary Holiday, Sports Spooktacular, Monster Matinee, Ghosts on the Go, Zoinks Camera Action, Route Scary Six, Monster Tails).  Like the other movies in the What's New Scooby Doo Series, it has four episodes that are very cute but the stories move quickly which is good for younger kids who get bored easily.  Two thumbs up for this Scooby Doo!  We were very excited since we saw some of the characters we've seen in other episodes (like the Golden Retriever Chrissy and the Secret Six puppies)...
